{"tid":1962381,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"悲報 潘志文腦中風離世","createTime":"2020-04-07T12:25:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-07T12:47:54.000Z","uid":13745,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"58511f97887bd3af033af96651aa4cf7d5893fa6","tid":1962381,"uid":13745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T12:25:15.000Z","msg":"2019年06月11日<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/政情/339569/前九龍城區議員潘志文-腦中風逝世-終年61歲\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85%2F339569%2F%E5%89%8D%E4%B9%9D%E9%BE%8D%E5%9F%8E%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E6%BD%98%E5%BF%97%E6%96%87-%E8%85%A6%E4%B8%AD%E9%A2%A8%E9%80%9D%E4%B8%96-%E7%B5%82%E5%B9%B461%E6%AD%B2&d=BHyrWEjohbhGCquuSPOYYiIHZ%2BXcjpWsQ0IfaGt1pN0%3D&h=882b2aac\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/政情/339569/前九龍城區議員潘志文-腦中風逝世-終年61歲</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n前民主黨九龍城區議員潘志文今日離世，其兒子和女兒今日透過短訊通知街坊，父親於今日下午因為腦中風在伊利沙伯醫院離世，離去時其家人及親人陪同在側。有九龍城區議員今日也收到潘志文離世的消息。潘的兒子昨天傍晚已透過短訊通知街坊，指父親病危，並透露是因為腦中風，情況不太樂觀 。今日下午三時，潘的兒子通知街坊，指父親已離世，感謝街坊們一路以來的愛護和照顧 ，潘的身後事會容後公佈。<br />\n<br />\n由2008年至2015年擔任九龍城土瓜灣南區議員的潘志文，被指2013年在辦事處強吻31歲女求助人，被裁定3項非禮罪成判囚兩個月。潘後經上訴脫罪，惟案件重審後他再次被裁定罪成，判囚3個月，他早前再提上訴，惟高院法院駁回其上訴，潘須即時入獄服刑。"},{"pid":"bbbdc0e4dc174b8123839b741a6bed1e26f815c7","tid":1962381,"uid":53172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T12:26:29.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"1fe6aea08f7d69d2fc30942b594b455c6768d38a","tid":1962381,"uid":58630,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T12:29:35.000Z","msg":"2019<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲以為係亞視嗰條友"},{"pid":"ea4398b7a17b5565bd42ba20603370495577226c","tid":1962381,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1fe6aea08f7d69d2fc30942b594b455c6768d38a","tid":1962381,"uid":58630,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T12:29:35.000Z","msg":"2019<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲以為係亞視嗰條友"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T12:38:25.000Z","msg":"Tvb now"},{"pid":"f74301492d9fe594211cdccc1e070723e72e8fa1","tid":1962381,"uid":271199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1fe6aea08f7d69d2fc30942b594b455c6768d38a","tid":1962381,"uid":58630,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T12:29:35.000Z","msg":"2019<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲以為係亞視嗰條友"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T12:44:03.000Z","msg":"Me too"},{"pid":"2296a67e3c194ebf9e5fc3a1a297c00b44e96df9","tid":1962381,"uid":349872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T12:47:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QRCayDM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQRCayDM.png&h=16ec138a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n樓主無講錯喎"}]}